OL,3,CThird person arrested over alleged
OL,4,Carson at former synagogue
OL,6,FA third person has been arrested over
OL,7,Fan alleged arson attack at a former
OL,8,Fsynagogue.
OL,10,FThe 31-year-old man was held in
OL,11,FLeyton, east London, on Tuesday on
OL,12,Fsuspicion of arson with intent to
OL,13,Fendanger life, the Metropolitan Police
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,FDamage was caused to gates and a lock
OL,17,Fat the site in Nelson Street,
OL,18,FWhitechapel, at around 5.10am on May 5.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/4
