CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1778775072
OL,3,CThird person arrested over alleged
OL,4,Carson at former synagogue
OL,6,FMoses Edwards 45, from Wanstead, has
OL,7,Falready been charged with arson with
OL,8,Fintent to endanger life and is next
OL,9,Fdue to appear in court at the Old
OL,10,FBailey on June 5.
OL,12,FA 52-year-old woman who was also
OL,13,Farrested in connection with the blaze
OL,14,Fwas bailed until August.
OL,16,FThe former synagogue is in the process
OL,17,Fof being bought by a Muslim community
OL,18,Fgroup with plans to convert it to a
OL,19,Fmosque and community centre.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
