PN,40603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1778775072
OL,3,CThird person arrested over alleged
OL,4,Carson at former synagogue
OL,6,FCommander Helen Flanagan, head of
OL,7,Fcounter-terrorism policing London,
OL,8,Fsaid:"The investigation team are
OL,9,Fworking at pace to arrest all those
OL,10,Fsuspected of being involved in the
OL,11,Farson attack on the former synagogue.
OL,13,F"I want to remind the public that,
OL,14,Fwith the threat level now raised to
OL,15,Fsevere, everyone can play their part
OL,16,Fto keep themselves and their
OL,17,Fcommunities safe. If you have concerns
OL,18,Fabout someone behaving suspiciously,
OL,19,Fplease report it to us. Your
OL,20,Finformation could help us save lives.
OL,26,@pD@FOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/4
