OL,3,CThird person arrested over alleged
OL,4,Carson at former synagogue
OL,6,F"Counter-terrorism officers also
OL,7,Fcontinue to work closely with our
OL,8,Fcolleagues in the Metropolitan Police
OL,9,Fin response to all the various
OL,10,Fincidents in recent months. We're
OL,11,Fproviding protective security advice
OL,12,Fand support to various organisations,
OL,13,Fcommunity venues and businesses."
